To run the project follow the steps below:

1. Install Galen Framework (http://galenframework.com/docs/getting-started-install-galen/)

2. Go to the root of the project.

3. To run only a test specification use the following command:

    galen check home-page.gspec --url "http://chip.us-east-1.awsdev-test.ngeo.com/" --size "1280x800" --include "desktop" --htmlreport "reports"

4. To run the entire test suite use the following command:

    galen test home-page.test --htmlreport "reports" 

More info about running tests with Galen Framework can be found here:
    http://galenframework.com/docs/reference-working-in-command-line/